 />\n<br />\n但要真係叫識Haskell, 就必需攪清monad呢個concept. 好多書都用好深既terms嚟explain what a monad is, 連高登神人Code4Food都係用咁既approach講解, 結果當然冇人知佢up乜春!<br />\n<br />\n但原來A picture is worth a thousand words真係至理名言, 用圖解好過你9up(睇完晒下面個圖解後, 冇乜maths底既我都開始明明地monad既運作, 唔錯!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ):<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Functors, Applicatives, And Monads In Pictures</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://adit.io/posts/2013-04-17-functors,_applicatives,_and_monads_in_pictures.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fadit.io%2Fposts%2F2013-04-17-functors%2C_applicatives%2C_and_monads_in_pictures.html&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=0c52b098\" target=\"_blank\">http://adit.io/posts/2013-04-17-functors,_applicatives,_and_monads_in_pictures.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nC4F有無過到嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n次次做CD ROM都睇唔明佢啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f9cd688eebb2b83c495245a576fbbf5ec74825","tid":135281,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:34:59.000Z","msg":"a monad is just a monoid in the category of endofunctor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}